comment:
* Represents a core networking event defined in package android.net.metrics.
 * Logged by IpConnectivityLog and managed by ConnectivityMetrics service.
 * {@hide}
 *

variables.name: timestamp
variables.comment: Time when this event was collected, as returned by System.currentTimeMillis().

variables.name: transports
variables.comment: Transports of the network associated with the event, as defined in NetworkCapabilities.

variables.name: netId
variables.comment: Network id of the network associated with the event, or 0 if unspecified.

variables.name: ifname
variables.comment: Name of the network interface associated with the event, or null if unspecified.
